{"title":"读报栏前","authors":["华君武　池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"读报栏前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华君武　画　池北偶　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不说假话讲真话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有官腔与虚夸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新闻信息多而快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评论文章笔生花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报喜报忧两不误，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时弊歪风敢鞭挞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可读可亲又可信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫人如何不爱它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板起面孔架子大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语言无味干巴巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文章不离党八股，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新闻多是老掉牙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈词滥调倒胃口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装腔作势忒肉麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可疑可畏又可厌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫人如何会爱它。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}